Arsenal Beats Udinese 2-1 to Reach Champions League Group Stage

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-24T20:38:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/arsenal-beats-udinese-2-1-to-reach-champions-league-group-stage.html
Arsenal defeated Udinese 2-1 to
advance to the group stage of soccer’s  Champions League .  Robin van Persie  and  Theo Walcott  scored as Arsenal
advanced 3-1 over the two-match playoff. The win sends the
Gunners to the group stage of  Europe ’s elite club competition
for the 14th consecutive season.  Benfica, Lyon, BATE Borisov and Viktoria Plzen also won
their playoffs to progess. The draw for the 32-group stage will
be held tomorrow in  Monaco .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  